    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-gray-900">Clocks Gallery</h1>
    <p class="mb-8 text-gray-600">Explore a collection of beautiful, modern, and experimental clocks. More coming soon!</p>
    <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
      <a href="/clocks/smartisan" class="clock-card">
